  "description": "You have to breathe underwater.",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/YoureAFishNow/BH_YAFN_OVERVIEW.png\" width=\"1133\" height=\"234\" /></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">You breathe underwater like a fish and you can't breathe above water. You have a time limit before you start dying when you are above water.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This is still in its development phase, suggestions are welcomed!</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Installation guide:</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Drop into mods folder on client and server (if you have a server)</span>\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/BfyBqJcR7x\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/social_assets/Bh_Discord.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"84\" style=\"text-align:center\"/></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\"><a href=\"mailto:limeshulkerbox@gmail.com\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/Better_Sodium/BH_LIME_EMAILCONTACT.png\" width=\"612\" height=\"151\" /></a></span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/lime\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/images/CF/YoureAFishNow/BH_YAFN_PROMOCODE.png\" width=\"1133\" height=\"183\" /></a></p>",
